snippet.title: the hammer in 99 nights is CRAZY cool!!
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

Niko shows Dad about the new hammer in 99 Nights in the forest on Roblox that you can use to steal cool items out of houses and take them home with you! He shows that you can steal a giant wolf head and take it wherever you want!

enjoy some A for Adley videos: https://www.youtube.com/c/AforAdleyLe...
have a blast with our A for Adley Shorts: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMHpfyAqrjrhn-mRS2bUL0g
share a best day ever with our family: https://www.youtube.com/user/Shonduras
